<item>
            <title>[SOLR-10094] /export handler (master only) loses the sort deep into the result set</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10094</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This bug only occurs in master, and was likely introduced with the new doc values iterator API which is slated for 7.0.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This bug was not caught by tests because there are no tests that have a large enough result set to catch the issue. As part of this ticket a test with a large enough result set will be added to reproduce the bug.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
